value.name: Tourist
value.overview: In this drama, each of three troubled women encounter a mysterious and charismatic man while traveling to Bangkok, Taipei, and Ho Chi Minh.

value.name: Tourist Police
value.overview: Tourist police officer Lera wants to investigate serious cases and dangerous crimes. But in her department, they are as rare as the good mood of the boss and the intelligence of her colleagues. Despite this, Lera essentially refuses the “cushy little town”, carefully prepared by her admiral father, and does not give up work in the special division for the protection of public order in Sochi. But just how to continue the service and protect the peace of guests of the city, contacting a thief and a swindler?

value.name: Jim Gaffigan: The Pale Tourist
value.overview: In The Pale Tourist, Gaffigan boldly goes where no stand-up comedian has gone before: everywhere. The two hour-long specials were filmed as part of Gaffigan's The Pale Tourist worldwide tour, in which he traveled the world--in each country meeting people, eating the food, and learning a bit about the history. He would then transform those experiences into a stand-up set of all-new material and perform it for locals and expatriates, before heading on to another destination and doing it all over again.

value.name: The Tourist
value.overview: When a man wakes up in the Australian outback with no memory, he must use the few clues he has to discover his identity before his past catches up with him.

value.name: Dark Tourist
value.overview: The definition of "tourism" is redefined as New Zealand filmmaker David Farrier sets his sights on the world of dark tourism.  From nuclear tourism in Japan to Pablo Escobar-inspired tourism in Columbia to frontier tourism in Turkmenistan, David visits the world’s grisly and offbeat destinations, meeting travelers drawn to them, and the people telling these stories day after day.

value.name: Tourist Trap
value.overview: Tourist Trap is a Welsh TV mockumentary-style comedy series following the fictional tourist board WOW Wales.

value.name: The Tourist Trap
value.overview: The location: a dream hotel on a Turkish island. Each week, a new group of tourists arrive from a different country – from England, Germany, Japan and the USA.

value.name: John Sergeant on the Tourist Trail
value.original_name: John Sergeant on the Tourist Trail

value.name: Indian Adaptation of The Tourist
value.overview: Indian adaptation of the original 2022 series starring Jamie Dornan.

value.name: The Accidental Tourist
value.overview: Stephen Mulhern is thrust out of his comfort zone to see if he can truly unearth the adventurer within. Ant & Dec are sending Stephen somewhere he has never been before, in an effort to help to test his resolve and push his boundaries.

value.name: An Idiot Abroad
value.overview: An Idiot Abroad is a British travel documentary television series broadcast on Sky1 and Science, as well as spin-off books published by Canongate Books, created by Ricky Gervais and Stephen Merchant and starring Karl Pilkington. The ongoing theme of both the television series and the books is that Pilkington has no interest in global travel, so Merchant and Gervais make him travel while they stay in the United Kingdom and monitor his progress.
